subsection.p:
So in two dimensions:

  \begin{array}{c|c}
  \text{place} \amp \dfrac1{r^p}\text{ is integrable when} \\ \hline
  \text{near }r=0 \amp p\lt 2\\[2mm]
  \text{near }r=\infty \amp p\gt 2
  \end{array}
